{"tid":1807442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方昨天下午在維園拘捕一名擊性武器","createTime":"2020-01-01T22:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T22:37:27.000Z","uid":71620,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb03f64f9269a7cf52599e31ab4f593352780cb","tid":1807442,"uid":71620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T22:37:02.000Z","msg":"警方昨日下午在維多利亞公園拘捕一名13歲男童，涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器及藏有工具可作非法用途。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，在他的背包檢獲一枝鐳射筆、伸縮棍、一個錘子、一把剪刀、一個防毒面罩、一包索帶及一罐黑色噴漆。被捕男童被暫控一項藏有攻擊性武器罪，及一項藏有工具可作非法用途。<br />\n<br />\n案件今日上午在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方昨日下午在灣仔區多個地點，拘捕4名年齡介乎16至19歲男子，涉嫌藏有工具可作非法用途，檢獲士巴拿、錘子、防毒面罩、手套、眼罩、玻璃樽及打火機。被捕男子正被扣留調查。<br />\n咁就兩條罪1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661b7386f8a4fb82dce222b2e4e98904e9ca552b","tid":1807442,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T22:37:27.000Z","msg":"美國聯署 3/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">欠600</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOABZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=a4ec10ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a>"}]}